comments: Kurucs (BKN) dislodges Williams III (BOS) from his position during the rebound affecting his ability to retrieve the ball.
Jordan (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Walker (BOS) and firms up on his left leg when contact occurs.
Walker (BOS) briefly grasps Jordan's (BKN) shorts as they disengage from the pick.
Williams (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Chiozza (BKN) and absorbs the contact.
Jordan (BKN) delivers contact to Williams III's (BOS) arm during his shooting motion on the shot at the rim.
Smart (BOS) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Jordan (BKN) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Kurucs (BKN) makes contact to the ball knocking it out of Theis' (BOS) hand as he attempts to gather for the inbounds pass.
Chiozza (BKN) briefly places his arm around Theis' (BOS) hip as they disengage from the pick.
Smart (BOS) places his arm to the front of LeVert (BKN) on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) slightly extends his arm into Brown (BOS) as he releases to retrieve the rebound.
Williams (BOS) makes incidental contact to LeVert's (BKN) arm after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Prince (BKN) makes contact to Theis (BOS) arm that affects his ability to control the loose ball.
Smart (BOS) makes marginal contact to LeVert's (BKN) body during the drive however LeVert (BKN) is able to move through the contact to make his desired pass.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) and firms up when contact occurs.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) briefly places his hand to the front of Walker (BOS) prior to the inbounds however, Walker (BOS) is able to move through the contact to retrieve the ball.
Williams (BOS) signals a timeout prior to stepping inbounds.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Walker (BOS).
Smart (BOS) makes contact to LeVert's (BKN) arm during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
